    "causal_summary": "HF cache was empty (48KB) post-reboot. The Setup A live swap (sub-phase 003) would block on first-use model downloads — ~~1.3GB combined — and risk hanging the MCP startup. We also did NOT know whether `@huggingface/transformers` v3.8.1 (the npm pkg HfLocalProvider uses) could actually load `google/embeddinggemma-300m`: Gemma3 architecture support in transformers.js is recent; the sentence-transformers config layer atop Gemma3 was the highest-risk unknown.",
